{
	// The workstations form a single line between begin and end
	all wstation: Workstation | wstation in end implies no wstation.succ
  	all wstation: Workstation | wstation in begin and wstation not in end 
  		implies end in wstation.^succ
  	all wstation: Workstation | no (wstation.^succ & wstation)
  	all wstation: Workstation | no wstation.succ implies wstation in end
  	all wstation: Workstation | some wstation.succ and no succ.wstation
  		implies wstation in begin
  	all wstation: Workstation | lone wstation.succ
}

{
	
  no w: Workstation | begin in w.succ

  
  no end.succ

  
  all w: Workstation - begin | one w1: Workstation | w in w1.succ

  
  all w: Workstation - end | one w1: Workstation | w1 in w.succ

  
  all w: Workstation | w in begin.*succ
}

{
    
    all ws: Workstation - end | one ws.succ

    
    no end.succ

    
    all ws: Workstation - begin | one w: Workstation | ws in w.succ

    
    no w: Workstation | begin in w.succ

    
    all ws: Workstation | ws in begin.*succ

    
    no ws: Workstation | ws in ws.^succ
}

{
	// The workstations form a single line between begin and end
	Workstation = begin.*succ
  	Workstation = end.*(~succ)
  	
  	all ws:Workstation - end - begin | one ws.succ and one ws.~succ
  
  	all ws:Workstation | ws not in ws.^succ
  
  	lone end.~succ
  	no end.succ
  
  	lone begin.succ
  	no begin.~succ
  
}

{
    
    Workstation = begin.*succ

    
    Workstation = end.*(~succ)

    
    all ws: Workstation - end | one ws.succ

    
    all ws: Workstation - begin | one ws.~succ

    
    no begin.~succ
    no end.succ
}

{
  
  no n: Workstation | n in begin.succ
  
  
  no end.succ
  
  
  all ws: Workstation - begin | one prec: Workstation | ws in prec.succ
  
  
  all ws: Workstation - end | one ws.succ
  
  
  all ws: Workstation | ws in begin.^succ
  
  
  end in begin.^succ
}

{
    
    all w : Workstation | w -> w not in succ

    
    one w1 : Workstation | begin -> w1 in succ

    
    one w2 : Workstation | w2 -> end in succ

    
    all w : Workstation - begin - end |
        (one w1 : Workstation | w -> w1 in succ) and
        (one w2 : Workstation | w2 -> w in succ)

    
    all w : Workstation | w in begin.*succ and end in w.*~succ

    
    no w : Workstation | w in w.^succ
}

{
	all x : Workstation | no x & x.^succ  

	all x : Workstation | lone x.succ
	all x : Workstation | lone succ.x

	all b : begin | b.^succ = Workstation  
	all b : begin | no succ.b  

	all e : end | ^succ.e = Workstation 
	all e : end | no e.succ   

}

{
	// The workstations form a single line between begin and end
	all wstation: Workstation | wstation in end implies no wstation.succ
  	all wstation: Workstation | wstation in begin and wstation not in end 
  		implies end in wstation.^succ
  	all wstation: Workstation | no (wstation.^succ & wstation)
  	all wstation: Workstation | no wstation.succ implies wstation in end
  	all wstation: Workstation | some wstation.succ and no succ.wstation
  		implies wstation in begin
  	all wstation: Workstation | one wstation.succ
}

{
	all x : Workstation | no x & x.^succ  

	all x : Workstation | lone x.succ
	all x : Workstation | lone succ.x

	all b : begin | b.~succ = Workstation  
	all b : begin | no succ.b  

	all e : end | ~succ.e = Workstation 
	all e : end | no e.succ   

	all x,y : Workstation | x!=y implies (no x.succ & y.succ)
	all x,y : Workstation | x!=y implies (no succ.x & succ.y)

}

{
	all x : Workstation | no x & x.^succ  

	all x : Workstation | lone x.succ
	all x : Workstation | lone succ.x

	all b : begin | b.~succ = Workstation  
	all b : begin | no succ.b  

	all e : end | ~succ.e = Workstation 
	all e : end | no e.succ   

}

{
    
    no ws: Workstation | ws in begin.~succ

    
    no end.succ

    
    all ws: Workstation - end | lone ws.succ

    
    all ws: Workstation - begin | one ws.~succ

    
    all ws: Workstation | ws in begin.^succ
}

{
	// The workstations form a single line between begin and end
	Workstation = begin.^succ
  	Workstation = end.^(~succ)
  	
  	all ws:Workstation - end - begin | one ws.succ and one ws.~succ
  
  	all ws:Workstation | ws not in ws.^succ
  
  	one end.~succ
  	no end.succ
  
  	one begin.succ
  	no begin.~succ
}

{
	
  no w: Workstation | begin in w.succ

  
  no end.succ

  
  all w: Workstation - begin | one w1: Workstation | w in w1.succ

  
  all w: Workstation - end | one w1: Workstation | w1 in w.succ

  
  all w: Workstation | w in begin.^succ
}

{
	// The workstations form a single line between begin and end

	all b : begin, w : Workstation | not w->b in succ  
	all e : end, w : Workstation | not e->w in succ 

	all b : begin, w : Workstation | not w in begin implies w in ^succ.b 
	all e : end, w : Workstation | not w in end implies e in ^succ.w 

	all w : Workstation | not w in ^succ.w  

	all x,y,z: Workstation  | (x->y in succ and x->z in succ) implies y=z 
	all x,y,z: Workstation  | (y->x in succ and z->x in succ) implies y=z 

		all e,b:Workstation | (e!=b and e in end and not e in begin and b in begin and not b in end)implies(e in ^succ.b)

}

{
	// The workstations form a single line between begin and end

	all b : begin, w : Workstation | not w->b in succ  
	all e : end, w : Workstation | not e->w in succ 

	all b : begin, w : Workstation | not w in begin implies w in ^succ.b 
	all e : end, w : Workstation | not w in end implies e in ^succ.w 

	all w : Workstation | not w in ^succ.w  

	all x,y,z: Workstation  | (x->y in succ and x->z in succ) implies y=z 
	all x,y,z: Workstation  | (y->x in succ and z->x in succ) implies y=z 

	all b:begin,e:end| b!=e implies (e in ^succ.b)

}

{
	all x : Workstation | no x & x.^succ  

	all x : Workstation | lone x.succ 
	all x : Workstation | lone succ.x  

	all b : begin | b.*succ = Workstation  
	all b : begin | no b.succ  

	all e : end | *succ.e = Workstation 
	all e : end | no e.succ   

	all x,y : Workstation | x!=y implies (no x.succ & y.succ)
	all x,y : Workstation | x!=y implies (no succ.x & succ.y)

}

{
	// The workstations form a single line between begin and end
	all b : begin, w : Workstation | not w->b in succ  
	all e : end, w : Workstation | not e->w in succ 

	all b : begin, w : Workstation | w!=b implies w in ^succ.b 
	all e : end, w : Workstation | w!=e implies e in ^succ.w 

	all w : Workstation | not w in ^succ.w  

	all x,y,z: Workstation  | (x->y in succ and x->z in succ) implies y=z 
	all x,y,z: Workstation  | (y->x in succ and z->x in succ) implies y=z 
  	all b:begin,e:end| b!=e implies (e in ^succ.b)

}

{
	// The workstations form a single line between begin and end
	all wstation: Workstation | wstation in end implies no wstation.succ
  	all wstation: Workstation | wstation in begin and wstation not in end 
  		implies end in wstation.^succ
  	all wstation: Workstation | no (wstation.succ & wstation)
  	all wstation: Workstation | no wstation.succ implies wstation in end
  	all wstation: Workstation | some wstation.succ and no succ.wstation
  		implies wstation in begin
  	all wstation: Workstation | no (wstation.^succ & wstation)
}

{
	some w1,w2 : Workstation | w1 in begin and w2 in end  
	all w1,w2 : Workstation | (w1 in begin and w2 in begin) implies (w1=w2) 
	all w1,w2 : Workstation | (w1 in end and w2 in end) implies (w1=w2) 

	all w : Workstation | not w->w in succ  
	all w1,w2:Workstation | (w1 in begin and w2!=w1) implies (not w2->w1 in succ) 
	all w1,w2:Workstation| (w2 in end and w1!=w2) implies (not w2->w1 in succ) 

	
	all w2:Workstation | (not w2 in begin and not w2 in end) implies (some w1,w3: Workstation |w1->w2 in succ and w2->w3 in succ)	

	all w1,w2,w3:Workstation | (w1->w2 in succ and w1->w3 in succ) implies (w2=w3)  
	all w1,w2,w3:Workstation | (w2->w1 in succ and w3->w1 in succ) implies (w2=w3)  
	all w1,w2:Workstation | (w1->w2 in succ) implies (not w2->w1 in succ) 

	
	all w1,w2:Workstation | (w1!=w2 and ((w1 in begin and w2 in end) or (w1 in end and w2 in begin))) implies ((w1->w2 in succ)or(w2->w1 in succ)) 

}

{
	some w1,w2 : Workstation | w1 in begin and w2 in end  
	all w1,w2 : Workstation | (w1 in begin and w2 in begin) implies (w1=w2) 
	all w1,w2 : Workstation | (w1 in end and w2 in end) implies (w1=w2) 

	all w : Workstation | not w->w in succ  
	all w1,w2:Workstation | (w1 in begin and w2!=w1) implies (not w2->w1 in succ) 
	all w1,w2:Workstation| (w2 in end and w1!=w2) implies (not w2->w1 in succ) 

	
	all w2:Workstation | (not w2 in begin and not w2 in end) implies (some w1,w3: Workstation | w1!=w3 and w1->w2 in succ and w2->w3 in succ)
	all w1,w2,w3:Workstation | (w1->w2 in succ and w1->w3 in succ) implies (w2=w3)  
	all w1,w2,w3:Workstation | (w2->w1 in succ and w3->w1 in succ) implies (w2=w3)  

	all w1,w2:Workstation | (w1!=w2 and ((w1 in begin and w2 in end) or (w1 in end and w2 in begin))) implies ((w1->w2 in succ)or(w2->w1 in succ)) 

}

{
	// The workstations form a single line between begin and end
	all ws: Workstation, wss: Workstation - ws |
  		ws in begin => ws not in wss.succ
  
  	all ws: Workstation |
  		ws in end => no ws.succ
  
  	all ws: Workstation - end |
  		one ws.succ
  
  	all ws: Workstation | 
  		ws not in ws.^succ
}

{
  
  no n: Workstation | n in begin.succ - begin
  
  
  no end.succ - end
  
  
  all ws: Workstation - begin | one prec: Workstation | ws in prec.succ
  
  
  all ws: Workstation - end | one ws.succ
  
  
  all ws: Workstation | ws in begin.^succ
}

{
	// The workstations form a single line between begin and end
	Workstation = begin.*succ
  	Workstation = end.*(~succ)
  	
  	all ws:Workstation - end - begin | one ws.succ and one ws.~succ
  
  	all ws:Workstation | ws not in ws.^succ
  
  	one end.~succ
  	no end.succ
  
  	one begin.succ
  	no begin.~succ
  
}

{
	all w : Workstation | not w->w in succ  

	all w:Workstation | w in begin implies (some w2:Workstation | w->w2 in succ)   
	all w1,w2,w3:Workstation | (w1 in begin and w1->w2 in succ and w1->w3 in succ) implies (w2=w3) 
	all w1,w2:Workstation | (w1 in begin and w2!=w1) implies (not w2->w1 in succ) 

	all w:Workstation | w in end implies (some w2:Workstation | w2->w in succ)  
	all w1,w2,w3:Workstation | (w1 in end and w2->w1 in succ and w3->w1 in succ) implies (w2=w3) 
	all w1,w2:Workstation| (w2 in end and w1!=w2) implies (not w2->w1 in succ) 


	all w2:Workstation | (not w2 in begin and not w2 in end) implies (some w1,w3: Workstation | w1!=w3 and w1->w2 in succ and w2->w3 in succ)

}

{
	// The workstations form a single line between begin and end
	Workstation = begin.*succ
  	Workstation = end.*(~succ)
  	
  	all ws:Workstation - end | one ws.succ
  	all ws:Workstation - begin | one ws.~succ
  
  	all ws:Workstation | ws not in ws.^succ
  
  	one end.~succ
  	no end.succ
  
  	one begin.succ
  	no begin.~succ
  
}

{
	
  no w: Workstation | begin in w.succ

  
  no end.succ

  
  all w: Workstation - begin | one w1: Workstation | w in w1.succ

  
  all w: Workstation - end | one w1: Workstation | w1 in w.succ

  no (begin.succ & begin)
}

{
	all w : Workstation | not w->w in succ

	all w:Workstation | w in begin implies (some w2:Workstation | w->w2 in succ)   
	all w1,w2,w3:Workstation | (w1 in begin and w1->w2 in succ and w1->w3 in succ) implies (w2=w3) 

	all w:Workstation | w in end implies (some w2:Workstation | w2->w in succ)  
	all w1,w2,w3:Workstation | (w1 in end and w2->w1 in succ and w3->w1 in succ) implies (w2=w3) 

	all w2:Workstation | (not w2 in begin and not w2 in end) implies (some w1,w3: Workstation | w1!=w3 and w1->w2 in succ and w2->w3 in succ)

}

{
	all w:Workstation | w in begin implies (some w2:Workstation | w->w2 in succ)   
	all w1,w2,w3:Workstation | (w1 in begin and w1->w2 in succ and w1->w3 in succ) implies (w2=w3) 

	all w:Workstation | w in end implies (some w2:Workstation | w2->w in succ)  
	all w1,w2,w3:Workstation | (w1 in end and w2->w1 in succ and w3->w1 in succ) implies (w2=w3) 

	all w2:Workstation | (not w2 in begin and not w2 in end) implies (some w1,w3: Workstation | w1!=w3 and w1->w2 in succ and w2->w3 in succ)

}

{
	some w1,w2 : Workstation | w1 in begin and w2 in end  
	all w1,w2 : Workstation | (w1 in begin and w2 in begin) implies (w1=w2) 
	all w1,w2 : Workstation | (w1 in end and w2 in end) implies (w1=w2) 

	all w : Workstation | not w->w in succ  
	all w1,w2:Workstation | (w1 in begin and w2!=w1) implies (not w2->w1 in succ) 
	all w1,w2:Workstation| (w2 in end and w1!=w2) implies (not w2->w1 in succ) 

	
	all w2:Workstation | (not w2 in begin and not w2 in end) implies (some w1,w3: Workstation | w1!=w3 and w1->w2 in succ and w2->w3 in succ)
	all w1,w2,w3:Workstation | (w1->w2 in succ and w1->w3 in succ) implies (w2=w3)  
	all w1,w2,w3:Workstation | (w2->w1 in succ and w3->w1 in succ) implies (w2=w3)  

}

{
	some w1,w2 : Workstation | w1 in begin and w2 in end  
	all w1,w2 : Workstation | (w1 in begin and w2 in begin) implies (w1=w2) 
	all w1,w2 : Workstation | (w1 in end and w2 in end) implies (w1=w2) 

	all w : Workstation | not w->w in succ  
	all w1,w2:Workstation | (w1 in begin and w2!=w1) implies (not w2->w1 in succ) 
	all w1,w2:Workstation| (w2 in end and w1!=w2) implies (not w2->w1 in succ) 

	
	

	all x:Workstation | some y,z:Workstation | (not x in begin and not x in end and y!=z and y!=x and z!=x) implies (y->x in succ and x->z in succ) 	

	all w1,w2,w3:Workstation | (w1->w2 in succ and w1->w3 in succ) implies (w2=w3)  
	all w1,w2,w3:Workstation | (w2->w1 in succ and w3->w1 in succ) implies (w2=w3)  

	
	all w1,w2:Workstation | (w1!=w2 and ((w1 in begin and w2 in end) or (w1 in end and w2 in begin))) implies ((w1->w2 in succ)or(w2->w1 in succ)) 

}

{
	some w1,w2 : Workstation | w1 in begin and w2 in end  
	all w1,w2 : Workstation | (w1 in begin and w2 in begin) implies (w1=w2) 
	all w1,w2 : Workstation | (w1 in end and w2 in end) implies (w1=w2) 

	all w : Workstation | not w->w in succ  
	all w1,w2:Workstation | (w1 in begin and w2!=w1) implies (not w2->w1 in succ) 
	all w1,w2:Workstation| (w2 in end and w1!=w2) implies (not w2->w1 in succ) 

	
	all w2:Workstation | (not w2 in begin and not w2 in end) implies (some w1,w3: Workstation |w1->w2 in succ and w2->w3 in succ)	

	all w1,w2,w3:Workstation | (w1->w2 in succ and w1->w3 in succ) implies (w2=w3)  
	all w1,w2,w3:Workstation | (w2->w1 in succ and w3->w1 in succ) implies (w2=w3)  

	
	all w1,w2:Workstation | (w1!=w2 and ((w1 in begin and w2 in end) or (w1 in end and w2 in begin))) implies ((w1->w2 in succ)or(w2->w1 in succ)) 

}

{
  

  
  no w: Workstation | w in begin.succ

  
  no w: Workstation | end in w.succ

  
  all w: Workstation - begin - end |
    one p: Workstation | p in w.succ

  
  all w: Workstation - begin - end |
    one s: Workstation | w in s.succ

  
  
  all w1, w2: Workstation | 
    (w1 in w2.succ) implies (w1 != begin and w1 != end and w2 != begin and w2 != end)
}
